'''彼得·哈蒙德'''（{{lang-en|Peter Haymond}}），汉名'''何孟德'''<ref>{{cite web |title=美国驻成都领事馆总领事何孟德做客重庆大学 |url=http://sie.cqu.edu.cn/info/1028/1234.htm |website=重庆大学国际学院 |accessdate=2020-07-25 |date=2012-12-19 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820085306/http://sie.cqu.edu.cn/info/1028/1234.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，曾任[[美国驻成都总领事馆|美国驻成都总领事馆]][[美国驻成都总领事列表|总领事]]，自2020年起担任{{tsl|en|List of ambassadors of the United States to Laos|美国驻老挝大使}}。

== 早年及教育 ==
哈蒙德获[[杨百翰大学|杨百翰大学]][[文学士|文学士]]及[[塔夫茨大學|塔夫茨大學]]{{tsl|en|Fletcher School of Law and Diplomacy|弗莱彻法律与外交学院}}法律与外交文学硕士和[[哲学博士|哲学博士]]<ref name="WHBio">[https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/president-donald-j-trump-announces-intent-nominate-individuals-key-administration-posts-14/ "President Donald J. Trump Announces Intent to Nominate Individuals to Key Administration Posts" White House, September 3, 2019] {{Wayback|url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/president-donald-j-trump-announces-intent-nominate-individuals-key-administration-posts-14/ |date=20190909214947 }} {{PD-notice}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://fletcher.tufts.edu/news-events/news/trump-taps-tufts-university-alum-be-next-ambassador-laos |title=Trump Taps Tufts University Alum to be Next Ambassador to Laos |date=2019-09-04 |website=fletcher.tufts.edu |access-date=2020-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223200326/https://fletcher.tufts.edu/news-events/news/trump-taps-tufts-university-alum-be-next-ambassador-laos |archive-date=2019-12-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 生涯 ==
1991年，何孟德加入{{le|美国外交勤务处|United States Foreign Service}}，担任{{le|高級外事官員|Senior Foreign Service}}，级别为[[公使銜參贊|公使銜參贊]]<ref name="Certificate">{{Cite web |url=https://www.state.gov/haymond-peter-m-lao-peoples-democratic-republic-september-2019/ |title=Haymond, Peter M. - Lao People's Democratic Republic - September 2019 |date=2019-09-25 |website=United States Department of State |language=en-US |access-date=2020-02-11 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030104920/https://www.state.gov/haymond-peter-m-lao-peoples-democratic-republic-september-2019/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此后担任[[美国国务院|美国国务院]][[美国国务院东亚和太平洋事务局|东亚和太平洋事务局]]局长、[[美国驻成都总领事馆|美国驻成都总领事馆]][[美国驻成都总领事列表|总领事]]、美国驻[[老挝|老挝]]大使馆[[使領館副館長|副館長]]。还曾任国务院经济和能源事务局（{{lang|en|Bureau of Economic and Energy Affairs}}）能源和商品处（{{lang|en|Division Chief in the Office of Energy and Commodities}}）处长，以及反恐协调處阿拉伯半岛负责人。之后任[[美國駐泰國大使館|美國駐泰國大使館]][[代办|代办]]<ref name="WHBio" />。在中国担任驻成都总领事期间，2012年参与处理了[[王立军事件|王立军事件]]。

2019年9月3日，[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]提名何孟德出任下任美国驻老挝大使，其提名于同年9月9日呈至[[美国参议院|美国参议院]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Seventeen Nominations and Two Withdrawals Sent to the Senate |url=https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/seventeen-nominations-two-withdrawals-sent-senate/ |website=The White House |accessdate=2020-07-25 |date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603152340/https://www.whitehouse.gov/presidential-actions/seventeen-nominations-two-withdrawals-sent-senate/ |archive-date=2020-06-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，本人于10月31日接受[[美国参议院外交委员会|外交委员会]]听证<ref name="Committee">{{Cite web |url=https://www.foreign.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/103119_Haymond_Testimony.pdf |title=Statement by Peter M. Haymond: Nominee for U.S. Ambassador to the Lao People’s Democratic Republic |date=2019-10-31 |website=Senate Foreign Relations Committee |access-date=2020-02-11 |archive-date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513020552/https://www.foreign.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/103119_Haymond_Testimony.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最终于12月19日以[[口头表决|口头表决]]形式获参议院通过<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.congress.gov/nomination/116th-congress/1047 |title=PN1047 - Nomination of Peter M. Haymond for Department of State, 116th Congress (2019-2020) |date=2019-12-19 |website=www.congress.gov |access-date=2020-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421162147/https://www.congress.gov/nomination/116th-congress/1047 |archive-date=2020-04-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年1月15日宣誓就职<ref>{{Cite tweet |number=1217567049712574469 |user=usasiapacific |title=Congratulations to Peter M. Haymond on his swearing in as the next U.S. Ambassador to #Laos.  Ambassador Haymond’s appointment underscores our commitment to a strong U.S.-Lao partnership, as Laos continues to play a crucial role in #ASEAN and the #IndoPacific region. |date=2020-01-15}}</ref>，2月7日到[[永珍|永珍]]向[[老挝人民民主共和国主席|老挝国家主席]][[本扬·沃拉吉|本扬·沃拉吉]]递交国书<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://la.usembassy.gov/category/press-releases/ |title=Press Releases |website=la.usembassy.gov |access-date=2020-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200502202122/https://la.usembassy.gov/category/press-releases/ |archive-date=2020-05-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 个人生活 ==
何孟德与妻子杜萨迪（{{lang|en|Dusadee}}）结婚30多年<ref name="Committee" />。他能说老挝语、泰语、普通话和法语<ref name="WHBio" />。

